"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?11/17/11545?source=see_link\">",
"      Cardiac resynchronization therapy in heart failure: Implantation and other considerations",
"     </a>",
"     <br/>",
"     <a class=\"medical medical_review\" href=\"UTD.htm?17/56/18314?source=see_link\">",
